Los Muertos Productions - a Carlos Don Diego Film

You know, a title like Vampire Chicks with Chainsaws leaves no room for manoeuvre. With a title like that you expect vampire chicks and you expect chainsaws and that, dear reader, is exactly what you get. As such you get what was expected . . . except . . . you didn't particularly expect a sci-fi background, with the source of the vampirism being extra terrestrial.
